name: Delicious Lohikeitto
desc: A classic soup from the frigid regions. The creamy chowder, smooth as flowing silk, envelops each ingredient in its smooth embrace. As you take your first sip, you feel a gentle, cozy warmth spread throughout you, as if a vivid, golden sunrise is taking place inside your stomach.

value.text: Restores 22% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 470 HP every 5s for 30s.
